Screenshots
Description
Coffee will keep your computer wide awake while your downloads or network transfers complete. Coffee prevents standby when your traffic speed on a selected network adapter is above the user configurable threshold.
Coffee Web Site
Categories
Internet, Monitoring, Power (UPS)
License
GNU General Public License version 3.0 (GPLv3)
Features
Donate Bitcoin: 16iFx5pSkazA9yvcwNTR8kCbQNzBxxm6HmPrevents standby when DownloadingPrevents standby when transfering files over the networkPrevents standby when using web installersProvides insight into why your computer wont enter sleepSaves you having to change the power setings to never and back again all the timeSaves you from having to redownload a file that will not resume after sleepmore to come....
